item.title: CVE-2020-6641|2024-08-04T09:11:04.624Z -- fortinet -- fortinet%20fortipresence
item.description: Two authorization bypass through user-controlled key vulnerabilities in the Fortinet FortiPresence 2.1.0 administration interface may allow an attacker to gain access to some user data via portal manager or portal users parameters.
